{"title":"没有时间","authors":["路工"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":2,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有时间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“学技术！”“学技术！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听你不知叫了多少遍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我问你学习怎么样？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你眼一挤关起来："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“啊哎，实在那有时间！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钟上针，不停转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过了一天又一天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一月一月过去了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春夏秋冬跟着撵……。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等你想起抓时间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早就落在大后边；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时你老革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你一套老经验……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你会到处吃不开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时间天天有，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"希望你醒过来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扔了包袱往前走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从头学起也有会的一天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席叫三五年学会经济工作。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请你当头等任务看待。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（转载自《人民铁道》）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}